Class TensoricDoubleSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.lang.TensoricSupport<java.lang.Double>

  • public class TensoricDoubleSupport
extends TensoricSupport<java.lang.Double>
    This is a convenience class which extends the Generic Tensoric support and already preconfigures it with the field of doubles and the default options.

    This class is intended to be subclasses
